Enum RECOProximity

    public enum RECOProximity
extends java.lang.Enum<RECOProximity>
implements android.os.Parcelable
    The RECOProximity represents the relative distance to a RECOBeacon.
    The RECOBeacon class uses RECOProximity.

    RECOProximity는 RECOBeacon 까지의 상대적인 거리를 나타냅니다.
    RECOProximity는 RECOBeacon 클래스에서 사용합니다.
